19 fees collected per quarter shall be remitted to the State Treasurer for
20 credit to the Waste Reduction and Recycling Incentive Fund. For purposes
21 of determining the total fees collected, any amount of fees rebated
22 pursuant to section 13-2042.01 shall be included as if the fees had not
23 been rebated, and the amount of the fees rebated pursuant to such section
24 shall be deducted from the amount to be credited to the Waste Reduction
