26 (b) From the fees credited to the Waste Reduction and Recycling
27 Incentive Fund under this subsection:
28 (i) Grants shall be awarded to counties, municipalities, and
29 agencies for the purposes of planning and implementing facilities and
30 systems to further the goals of the Integrated Solid Waste Management
31 Act. The grant proceeds shall not be used to fund landfill closure site
